  <h1>Quickstart</h1>
  <p class="muted">Minimal examples for calling the API.</p>

  <h2>1) Get randomness</h2>
  <pre><code>curl -sS "https://api.re4ctor.com/v1/random?n=32&amp;fmt=hex" \
  -H "X-API-Key: YOUR_API_KEY"</code></pre>

  <h2>2) Browser usage (CORS)</h2>
  <p>Use <code>X-API-Key</code> header. Preflight is supported for allowed origins.</p>

  <h2>3) OpenAPI</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="https://api.re4ctor.com/openapi.json">OpenAPI JSON</a></li>
    <li><a href="/api/">Interactive API playground</a></li>
  </ul>

